<div class="center">
<div class="floatnone"><a href="/wiki/File:Niellim-closeup.png" class="image" title="Closeup of the area where Niellim is spoken."><img alt="Closeup of the area where Niellim is spoken." src="http://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/1/18/Niellim-closeup.png/300px-Niellim-closeup.png" width="300" height="323" /></a></div>
